{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"readyTime"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gint64","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gint64"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the monotonic time is in the past (as it"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"always will be if ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"readyTime"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"code":"0","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":") then the source will be","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dispatched immediately."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"readyTime"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-1"},{"type":"text","text":" then the source is never woken up on the basis"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the passage of time."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dispatching the source does not reset the ready time.  You should do"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"so yourself, from the source dispatch function."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that if you have a pair of sources where the ready time of one"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"suggests that it will be delivered first but the priority for the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"other suggests that it would be delivered first, and the ready time","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for both sources is reached during the same main context iteration,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"then the order of dispatch is undefined.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is a no-op to call this function on a [struct","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source"},{"text":"] which has","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"already been destroyed with [method"},{"code":"GLib.Source.destroy","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"].","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This API is only intended to be used by implementations of [struct","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"]."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Do not call this API on a [struct","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source"},{"text":"] that you did not create.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a source to be dispatched when the given monotonic time is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"reached (or passed)."}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"extendedModule":"GLib","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"readyTime","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gint64","text":"gint64","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"set(readyTime:)","externalID":"s:4GLib14SourceProtocolPAAE3set9readyTimeys5Int64V_tF::SYNTHESIZED::s:4GLib6SourceC","role":"symbol"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source\/set(readyTime:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source\/SourceProtocol-Implementations"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/source\/set(readytime:)"]}],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/Source":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source","role":"symbol","title":"Source","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/source","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Source","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Source","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"code":"GSource","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" struct is an opaque data type","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"representing an event source."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/Source/set(readyTime:)":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"readyTime","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"gint64","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gint64","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source\/set(readyTime:)","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a source to be dispatched when the given monotonic time is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reached (or passed).","type":"text"}],"title":"set(readyTime:)","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/source\/set(readytime:)"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/Source/SourceProtocol-Implementations":{"title":"SourceProtocol Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/source\/sourceprotocol-implementations","type":"topic","role":"collectionGroup","kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Source\/SourceProtocol-Implementations","abstract":[]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","title":"GLib","role":"collection","url":"\/documen